latedentries\">\n                            jump to other results\n                        </a></div></div><ol class=\"sense_single\" htag=\"ol\"><li class=\"sense\" fkox5000=\"y\" htag=\"li\" id=\"accountable_sng_1\" hclass=\"sense\" fkcefr=\"c1\"><span class=\"sensetop\" hclass=\"sensetop\" htag=\"span\"><span class=\"def\" hclass=\"def\" htag=\"span\">responsible for your decisions or actions and expected to explain them when you are asked</span></span><ul class=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\" hclass=\"examples\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">The state spends taxpayers’ money and should be <span class=\"cl\">held accountable</span>.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"> <span class=\"cf\" hclass=\"cf\" htag=\"span\">accountable to somebody</span> <span class=\"x\">Politicians are ultimately accountable to the voters.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"> <span class=\"cf\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"cf\">accountable for something</span> <span class=\"x\">Someone must be <span class=\"cl\">held accountable</span> for the killings.</span></li></ul> <span class=\"xrefs\" htag=\"span\" xt=\"cp\" hclass=\"xrefs\"><span class=\"prefix\">compare</span> <a class=\"Ref\" href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/unaccountable\" title=\"unaccountable definition\"><span class=\"xr-g\" bord=\"n\" href=\"unaccountable_e\"><span class=\"xh\">unaccountable</span></span></a></span><div class=\"collapse\" hclass=\"collapse\" htag=\"div\"><span class=\"unbox\" id=\"accountable_unbox_1\" unbox=\"extra_examples\"><span class=\"box_title\">Extra Examples</span><ul class=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\" hclass=\"examples\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Local authorities should be publicly accountable to the communities they serve.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Politicians are accountable to Parliament.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Senior managers are directly accountable to the Board of